cu.explanation_en: Invalid IP address format with octet value exceeding 255, causing unreachable NGU interface routing.

du.explanation_en: Mismatched frequency bands between DL (78) and UL (79), causing frequency misalignment and potential system faults.
du.explanation_zh: 上下行頻率帶不匹配（DL 為 78，UL 為 79），導致頻率錯位並可能引起系統故障。
